description: Unable to collect firmware inventory from the server. The firmware inventory in OneView may not be up to date.

eventDetails.eventItemValue: Ensure that the network connectivity to the iLO is in a healthy condition. The health can be viewed from the server hardware page. If there are any active alerts in the server hardware activity page, follow the resolutions specified in them. Refresh the server in order to fetch the inventory again. If the problem persists, contact your authorized support representative and provide them with a OneView support dump and the AHS logs from the iLO.
